query:
UPDATE pm_user_operations 
                SET org_id = COALESCE(pm_user_operations.org_id, $1),
                    paymaster_mode = COALESCE(pm_user_operations.paymaster_mode, $2),
                    paymaster_id = COALESCE(pm_user_operations.paymaster_id, $3),
                    credential_id = COALESCE(pm_user_operations.credential_id, $4),
                    metadata = metadata || $5::jsonb,
                    usd_amount = COALESCE(usd_amount, $6),
                    native_usd_price = COALESCE(native_usd_price, $7),
                    account_deployed = COALESCE(account_deployed, $8)
                WHERE user_op_hash = $9
